TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {20166=Sara Elizabeth (Betty) Galloway On April 8, 2012, Sara Elizabeth (Betty) Ellis Galloway passed away in Richland, Wash. Betty was predeceased in death by her husband the Rev. Dr. Edward D. Galloway, who passed in 1970. Edward and Betty were married in 1945. Betty was born Feb, 9, 1919, in Owen County to Ernest Ellis and Maude Roland Ellis. Maude also died on an Easter Sunday., 25831=The Owenton News Herald | circulation@owentonnewsherald.com | 502-484-3431 P.O. Box 219, 154 W.
